          <article class="panel wide">
            <h2>Booking Contact</h2>

            <p>
              For bookings, guest mixes, press requests or selected collaborations, use the booking page or contact directly by email.
            </p>

            <a class="link-row" href="/booking">
              <strong>Request Booking</strong>
              <span>Form</span>
            </a>

            <a class="link-row" href="mailto:itchylemon.booking@gmail.com">
              <strong>itchylemon.booking@gmail.com</strong>
